platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Beautifully designed and powerful to use, Flighty is a first-class flight tracker for those on the move. The app offers detailed flight maps, live tracking, and delay forecasting  but the real magic is the perfectly timed notifications that keep you up to date and stress-free.
